
INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS

Please see the Readme.<your-platform> file in the doc/ subdirectory for 
installation instructions:

  Linux users:                   see doc/Readme.Unix
  MSVC users on Windows:         see doc/Readme.MSVC
  Cygwin/MinGW users (Windows):  see doc/Readme.Cygwin and Readme.MinGW

If you find an error or missing information in these documents, please help us
improve them by letting us know about it.

Andras

